<li id="cite_note-53"><b><a href="#cite_ref-53" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMarkowsky1992">Markowsky, George (January 1992). "<a href="http://www.umcs.maine.edu/~markov/GoldenRatio.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.umcs.maine.edu/~markov/GoldenRatio.pdf" rel="nofollow">Misconceptions about the Golden Ratio</a>" (PDF). <i>College Mathematics Journal</i> <b>23</b> (1): 1<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.umcs.maine.edu/~markov/GoldenRatio.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.umcs.maine.edu/~markov/GoldenRatio.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.umcs.maine.edu/~markov/GoldenRatio.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Misconceptions+about+the+Golden+Ratio&amp;rft.jtitle=College+Mathematics+Journal&amp;rft.aulast=Markowsky&amp;rft.aufirst=George&amp;rft.au=Markowsky%2C+George&amp;rft.date=January+1992&amp;rft.volume=23&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.pages=1&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.umcs.maine.edu%2F%7Emarkov%2FGoldenRatio.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Golden_ratio"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
